Requirements:
Automation tests can be run on Windows and support Ukrainian version of the site, so vpn should be used if you are outside Ukraine

Preconditions:
1) install python 3.9
2) install required libraries using the next command run 'pip install -r requirements.txt'
3) install the latest Chrome

How to run:
Use 'pytest' command to run all tests
Use 'pytest -s tests\log_in --html=report.html' command to run all tests from specified folder
Use 'pytest tests\log_in\test_login_negative.py --html=report.html' command to run all tests from specified file

Notice:
Reports are stored "C:/Users/Your name/sweet_tv/report.html"
